title: Shovana Narayan - The Sterling Book of Indian Classical Dances -
description: Shovana Narayan - The Sterling Book of Indian Classical Dances - 2004 epub A presentation of the eight classical dance styles - Bharatanatyam, Kathak, Kathakali, Kuchipudi, Manipuri, Mohiniyattam, Odissi and Sattriya, through a concise portrayal of the background of each dance form, the salient features, format of presentation, music and costume. Paperback: 78 pages Publisher: New Dawn Press; UK ed. edition (4 December 2004) Language: English ISBN-10: 184557169X https://www.amazon.in/Sterling-Book-Indian-Classical-Dances/dp/184557169X
